Hunt for van stolen in Birstall
nodes.summary:
A man had his van stolen while making a delivery.

The driver got out of the van through the passenger door to make a delivery at around 11.20am on Monday, leaving the keys in the ignition, when another van pulled up alongside it.

A suspect got into the van through the driver’s door and started the van. Its owner tried to reopen the passenger door but the suspect had locked it, then drove away.
